		<title>Understand and Optimize AWS Data Transfer Charges for Splunk Cloud on AWS Ingestion</title>
		<link>https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/apn/understand-and-optimize-aws-data-transfer-charges-for-splunk-cloud-on-aws-ingestion/</link>
				
