&lt;h2&gt;Heimdall Data – AWS Partner Spotlight&lt;/h2&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Heimdall Data is an AWS Partner&lt;/strong&gt; with Service Ready designations for Amazon RDS and Amazon Redshift. Heimdall Data offers a database proxy that offloads SQL and improves database scale while securing database access. Proxy deployment does not require code changes.&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://partnercentral.awspartner.com/PartnerConnect?id=001E000001d9pndIAA&amp;amp;source=Blog"&gt;Contact Heimdall Data&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href="https://partners.amazonaws.com/partners/001E000001d9pndIAA/Heimdall%20Data"&gt;Partner Overview&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href="https://aws.amazon.com/marketplace/seller-profile?id=ca9b43e9-af75-4d5b-bf22-89b138927902"&gt;AWS Marketplace&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
							
		
